  "prompt": "What is a suitable solar panel installation provider in San Jose, California CA?",
  "response": "There are several reputable solar panel installation providers in San Jose, California. Here are a few options to consider:\n\n1. **Sunrun**: Sunrun is one of the largest residential solar companies in the United States, offering solar panel installation, leasing, and purchase options.\n\n2. **Sungevity**: Sungevity provides comprehensive solar solutions, including design, installation, and maintenance services.\n\n3. **Tesla Solar**: Tesla offers solar panels and solar roof installations, known for their sleek design and integration with Tesla Powerwall for energy storage.\n\n4. **Vivint Solar**: Vivint Solar specializes in custom solar solutions for homes, offering lease and purchase options along with professional installation.\n\n5. **SolarCity**: Although it is now integrated under Tesla, SolarCity has a strong presence in San Jose and provides various solar energy solutions.\n\n6. **PetersenDean Roofing & Solar**: This company offers both roofing and solar installation services, ensuring that your roof is in good condition to support solar panels.\n\n7. **Semper Solaris**: Semper Solaris provides solar panel installation, battery storage, and roofing services, with a focus on customer satisfaction and veteran support.\n\nBefore choosing a provider, it's advisable to request quotes, check customer reviews, and ensure the company is licensed and certified in solar installations. Additionally, consider factors like warranty, financing options, and post-installation support.",
